《'''卧底老板'''》（{{lang|en|Undercover Boss}}）是一部获得了[[艾美奖|艾美奖]]的[[美国|美国]][[真人秀|真人秀]]节目，始于2010年，它是源自于[[卧底老板|同名的英国电视剧节目]]，并由同一制作公司兰姆伯特摄影棚（Studio Lambert）负责制作。每一集都围绕一名在大型企业中担任高级管理职位的人展开，主人公决定作为一名新近员工在公司中卧底，以找出企业存在的不足。第一季于2009年制作，共9集，并于2010年2月7日开始在[[哥伦比亚广播公司|哥伦比亚广播公司]]播出。<ref name="ausv">{{cite web|url=http://thetubetv.net/undercover-boss-coming-to-ten/|title=Undercover Boss coming to Ten|publisher=What's-On-The-Tube.com.au|date=2010-08-04|accessdate=2010-08-08|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20101020101102/http://thetubetv.net/undercover-boss-coming-to-ten/|archivedate=2010-10-20}}</ref> 根据Advertising Age的说法，出现在该节目中的公司都被保证其品牌形象不会受损。<ref>{{cite web |last=Bryson |first=Emily |url=http://adage.com/article/news/7-eleven-hooters-risk-undercover-boss/142119/ |title=7-Eleven, Hooters, Others Take Risk in 'Undercover Boss' |publisher=Adage.com |date=2010-02-15 |accessdate=2013-04-20 |archive-date=2015-05-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150502091734/http://adage.com/article/news/7-eleven-hooters-risk-undercover-boss/142119/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

该剧集大获成功，首播集的观众人数为3860万人，收视率为32%。<ref name="ep1r2">{{cite web|url=http://tvbythenumbers.com/2010/02/09/tv-ratings-super-bowl-xliv-post-game-and-undercover-boss-dominate-weekly-viewing/41481|title=TV Ratings: Super Bowl XIV post game and Undercover Boss dominate weekly viewing|publisher=TV-By-The-Numbers.com|date=2010-08-04|accessdate=2010-08-08|archive-date=2010-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100212201315/http://tvbythenumbers.com/2010/02/09/tv-ratings-super-bowl-xliv-post-game-and-undercover-boss-dominate-weekly-viewing/41481|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 该节目的第一季是2009-10电视播出季中最受欢迎的新节目，平均观众人数为1770万人。<ref>{{cite web|title=CBS ANNOUNCES FOUR COMPANIES PARTICIPATING IN THE SECOND SEASON OF THE EMMY AWARD-NOMINATED SERIES, "UNDERCOVER BOSS"|url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2010/07/28/cbs-announces-four-companies-participating-in-the-second-season-of-the-emmy-award-nominated-series-undercover-boss/20100728cbs02/|publisher=The Futon Critic|accessdate=2010-09-12|author=CBS|date=2010-07-28}}</ref>

第二季的平均观众人数为1215.8万人，<ref>{{cite web |last=Andreeva |first=Nellie |url=http://www.deadline.com/2011/05/full-2010-11-season-series-rankers/ |title=Full 2010-2011 TV Season Series Rankings |publisher=Deadline.com |date= |accessdate=2013-04-20 |archive-date=2012-08-09 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/69mfyVjkW?url=http://www.deadline.com/2011/05/full-2010-11-season-series-rankers/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 而第三季由于从周日档移到了观众较少的周五晚间档，平均收视人数为934.7万人。<ref>{{cite web |last=Andreeva |first=Nellie |url=http://www.deadline.com/2012/05/full-2011-2012-tv-season-series-rankings/ |title=Full 2011-2012 TV Season Series Rankings |publisher=Deadline.com |date= |accessdate=2013-04-20 |archive-date=2014-04-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140424020321/http://www.deadline.com/2012/05/full-2011-2012-tv-season-series-rankings/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 2012年3月，哥伦比亚广播公司宣布续订第4季，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2012/03/14/good-wife-undercover-boss-renewed_n_1345076.html |title='The Good Wife,' 'Blue Bloods,' 'Undercover Boss' And More Get Early Pickups From CBS |publisher=Huffingtonpost.com |date=2012-03-14 |accessdate=2013-04-20 |archive-date=2016-09-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160910163815/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2012/03/14/good-wife-undercover-boss-renewed_n_1345076.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> 第5季的续订则在2013年3月宣布。<ref>{{cite web |author=Post to Facebook |url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/tv/2013/03/27/cbs-tv-shows-renewed/2025851/ |title=CBS renews top shows |publisher=Usatoday.com |date=2013-03-28 |accessdate=2013-04-20 |archive-date=2019-12-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191215065121/https://www.usatoday.com/story/life/tv/2013/03/27/cbs-tv-shows-renewed/2025851/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

